---
---
<section id="contato" class="section-padding bg-[#1E293B] relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Tech patterns -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.05] pointer-events-none">
     <svg width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
           <pattern id="grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
              <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
           </pattern>
        </defs>
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid)" />
     </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-[#2563EB]">
        Consulta Inicial
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-10 text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.95] text-white sm:text-7xl tracking-tighter">
        O Sorriso Que Você <br />
        <span class="text-[#2563EB]">Sempre Sonhou</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-10 text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-400 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Dê o primeiro passo para uma nova fase da sua vida. Agende sua avaliação digital e descubra o que a odontologia moderna pode fazer por você.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10">
        <a href="https://wa.me/5511999999999" target="_blank" class="btn-tech px-14 py-6 text-sm">
          Agendar Via WhatsApp
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8 text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">
          <span>Atendimento VIP</span>
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#2563EB]"></span>
          <span>Bela Vista, São Paulo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
